[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/toxic">Toxic</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>A move that leaves the foe badly poisoned. The poison damage worsens every turn.</p>